asset.hookText: It started in the mind of a free spirit. Then it became a tangle of sketches. Then it became the new Nike Free Run+. Mark Miner and his creative process are as uninhibited as the Nike Free collection he designed. Get a glimpse at what happens before an idea becomes reality.
